# Implementation Plan - App Logo and Icon Integration

This plan outlines the steps to generate a professional logo for CirclCare and integrate it across all platforms (iOS, Android, Web).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Please review the generated logo below. If you'd like any changes to the design, colors, or style, let me know before I proceed with the integration.

