## Proposed Changes

### Assets

#### [NEW] [icon.png](file:///c:/Users/Jahan/Documents/circlcare/assets/images/icon.png)
- Replace the existing generic icon with the new CirclCare logo.

#### [NEW] [android-icon-foreground.png](file:///c:/Users/Jahan/Documents/circlcare/assets/images/android-icon-foreground.png)
- Create a foreground version of the logo specifically for Android's adaptive icon system.

#### [NEW] [splash-icon.png](file:///c:/Users/Jahan/Documents/circlcare/assets/images/splash-icon.png)
- Update the splash screen icon to match the new branding.

#### [NEW] [favicon.png](file:///c:/Users/Jahan/Documents/circlcare/assets/images/favicon.png)
- Generate a small-scale version for the web favicon.

### Configuration

#### [MODIFY] [app.json](file:///c:/Users/Jahan/Documents/circlcare/app.json)
- Ensure all paths are correctly pointing to the new assets.
- Adjust `adaptiveIcon.backgroundColor` to complement the new logo design.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- No automated tests required for asset replacement, but I will verify the `app.json` structure remains valid.

### Manual Verification
- I will check the file existence and paths.
- If possible, I will describe the visual consistency across the generated assets.
